<div class="NavHead" style="font-size: 105%; background: transparent; text-align: left; padding:0.2em; margin:0px; line-height:normal; font-size:90%; height:auto;;">Philosophy and<br />
history of science</div>
<div class="NavContent" style="font-size: 105%; padding: 0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align: center; padding:2px; margin:0px; line-height:normal; font-size: 90%; height:auto;;">
