<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Science_policy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Government versus academic control of research direction">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Government_versus_academic_control_of_research_direction">Government versus academic control of research direction</span></h3>
<div class="rellink relarticle mainarticle">Main article: <a href="/wiki/Haldane_principle" title="Haldane principle">Haldane principle</a></div>
<table class="metadata plainlinks ambox mbox-small-left ambox-content" style="">
