<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Science_policy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Science and the public">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Science_and_the_public">Science and the public</span></h2>
<div class="rellink relarticle mainarticle">Main articles: <a href="/wiki/Public_awareness_of_science" title="Public awareness of science">Public awareness of science</a> and <a href="/wiki/Science_outreach" title="Science outreach">Science outreach</a></div>
