<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Science_policy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10" title="Edit section: Science and politics">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="Science_and_politics">Science and politics</span></h2>
<div class="rellink relarticle mainarticle">Main articles: <a href="/wiki/Evidence-based_policy" title="Evidence-based policy">Evidence-based policy</a> and <a href="/wiki/Politicization_of_science" title="Politicization of science">Politicization of science</a></div>
<table class="metadata plainlinks ambox mbox-small-left ambox-content" style="">
<tr>
<td class="mbox-image"><img alt="Wiki letter w.svg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/6/6c/Wiki_letter_w.svg/23px-Wiki_letter_w.svg.png" width="23" height="23" /></td>
<td class="mbox-text" style=""><span class="mbox-text-span"><b>This section is empty.</b> <small>You can help by <a class="external text" href="//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Science_policy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10">adding to it</a>.</small></span></td>
</tr>
